  "text": "http://www.behavioralandbrainfunctions.com/content/4/1/44 ential expression of immune gene sets for both classification systems. As suggested by Efron and Tibshirani [CITATION_1] the performance of these gene sets was also compared to that obtained with randomly populated sets of the same size. A null distribution was computed from the analysis of 1000 instances of random gene selections and 1000 random permutations of the diagnostic labels.",
